        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-05-16T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-05-16T10:00:00-05:00" n="746" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d746">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.50/5–1645: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-05-16T17:00:00+02:00">May 16, 1945—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received May 16—3:59 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4875. ReDepts 3723, May 12, 1 p.m. Your suggestion regarding formal invitation to
                    Danish Govt to attend meetings of ECO and EECE is agreed to by the Foreign
                    Office which is issuing the invitation immediately.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Winant</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
